OL,3,CHow Jersey parents can claim more than
OL,4,C#6,000 for childcare in 2026
OL,6,FFamilies in Jersey can claim up to
OL,7,F#6,270 per school year toward
OL,8,Fchildcare costs under a new universal
OL,9,Ffunding scheme for children aged two
OL,10,Fto three.
OL,12,FThe initiative aims to ease financial
OL,13,Fpressure on households after a
OL,14,Fgovernment survey revealed that 90% of
OL,15,Fparticipating parents identified
OL,16,Faffordability as a "top concern".
