OL,3,CHow Jersey parents can claim more than
OL,4,C#6,000 for childcare in 2026
OL,6,FSet to benefit around 700 families,
OL,7,FJersey's Education Minister, Deputy
OL,8,FRob Ward, said: "This scheme
OL,9,Frepresents a significant step forward
OL,10,Fin supporting families and investing
OL,11,Fin the early development of our
OL,12,Fyoungest children."
OL,14,FAs part of the scheme, parents will
OL,15,Fneed to pay for their childcare costs
OL,16,Fupfront; however, with proof of
OL,17,Fpurchase, families can apply to be
OL,18,Freimbursed.
