OL,3,CHow Jersey parents can claim more than
OL,4,C#6,000 for childcare in 2026
OL,6,FTo be eligible, childcare must be
OL,7,Fprovided by a registered provider,
OL,8,Fsuch as a private nursery or a
OL,9,Fchildminder.
OL,11,FDeputy Rob Ward explained: "Payments
OL,12,Fwill be made in arrears, in up to
OL,13,Fthree instalments, upon proof of
OL,14,Fpurchase from a registered provider."
OL,16,FAdditional support is available for
OL,17,Ffamilies on Income Support, and the
OL,18,FJersey Child Care Trust (JCCT) can
OL,19,Fassist those unable to pay in advance.
