OL,3,CHow Jersey parents can claim more than
OL,4,C#6,000 for childcare in 2026
OL,6,F"It reflects our determination to
OL,7,Fprovide children with the best
OL,8,Fpossible start in life and to address
OL,9,Faffordability, which over 90% of
OL,10,Fparents surveyed identified as their
OL,11,Ftop concern," Deputy Ward added.
OL,13,F"This universal approach means there
OL,14,Fare no working, income, or residency
OL,15,Fconditions, ensuring that every
OL,16,Feligible family can benefit.
