OL,3,CHow Jersey parents can claim more than
OL,4,C#6,000 for childcare in 2026
OL,6,F"We anticipate that approximately 700
OL,7,Ffamilies will benefit in 2026, with
OL,8,Fresource implications of up to #4.5
OL,9,Fmillion in 2026 and #5.3 million in
OL,10,F2027, as approved in the Government
OL,11,FPlan.
OL,13,F"This investment is about more than
OL,14,Faffordability; it is about supporting
OL,15,Fchild development, enabling parents to
OL,16,Fwork or study, and strengthening the
OL,17,Ffoundations for lifelong learning."
