OL,3,CHow Jersey parents can claim more than
OL,4,C#6,000 for childcare in 2026
OL,6,FChief Executive Officer of Jersey
OL,7,FChild Care Trust, Fiona Vacher, said:
OL,8,F"This new funding scheme will make a
OL,9,Freal difference to families across
OL,10,FJersey.
OL,12,F"By reducing the financial barriers to
OL,13,Fchildcare, parents can focus on work,
OL,14,Fstudy, and family life, while children
OL,15,Fbenefit from high-quality education
OL,16,Fand care."
OL,18,FApplications for the scheme will open
OL,19,Fonline in February, and its first
OL,20,Fpayments will be made by April.
